Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.51,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K28}立{\K45}ち{\K49}上{\K40}が{\K58}る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.51,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.55,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K18}こ{\K26}の{\K28}世{\K39}は{\K37}弱{\K71}肉{\K65}強{\K37}食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.55,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個弱肉強食的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:49.44,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K26}据{\K34}え{\K20}膳{\K85}食{\K28}う{\K34}よ{\K43}り
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:49.44,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其坐享其成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.25,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K37}血{\K80}潮{\K87}奮っ{\K47}て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.25,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如憑著一腔激蕩熱血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.37,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K26}つ{\K53}か{\K42}み{\K33}と{\K56}れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.37,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拼命奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.10,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K66}賭{\K16}け{\K34}ろ{\K30}プ{\K40}ラ{\K34}イ{\K47}ド
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.10,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上尊嚴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.84,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K16}死{\K44}ぬ{\K30}ま{\K35}で{\K139}狼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.84,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至死都是一匹狼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:06.85,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K38}負{\K32}け{\K71}犬{\K32}に{\K36}な{\K46}る{\K30}つ{\K25}も{\K17}り{\K55}は{\K27}な{\K71}い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:06.85,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從不打算成為喪家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.05,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K69}汗{\K37}は{\K29}ス{\K44}パ{\K25}イ{\K50}ス
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.05,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗水是調味料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.81,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K57}傷{\K55}跡{\K106}輝{\K47}く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.81,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕在閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:17.46,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K71}勝{\K44}利{\K37}の{\K63}味{\K45}を{\K34}か{\K31}み{\K49}し{\K32}め{\K43}て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:17.46,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細咀嚼著勝利的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:21.20,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K43}次{\K30}の{\K23}ス{\K41}テー{\K16}ジ{\K201}へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:21.20,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向下一個舞臺邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在貼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是西區的超市的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數字代表便當變成半價的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我個人推薦這兩處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克商場和常磐超市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道霍克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是昨晚你們在那戰斗過的那家超市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說兩邊都很容易陷入激戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相應地 也是能讓你們得到教育的好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這兩家超市都是我的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我就暫時先到別的地方去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克商場的半價神 油神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他貼完以前都不可以輕舉妄動是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗有幾條規則
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 不能在半價神離開賣場前出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 貼完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在半價神離開賣場前出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 佐藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.55,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}炸豬扒便當
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能獵取超過當晚自己吃的分量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 這就是「狼」的戰斗方式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有著各種各樣的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是全部都能歸結於這一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守禮儀 賭上尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下一家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 小狗們 今天過來這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 就是「狗」的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 光頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你又...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事 事實上就是這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 老頭要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這家超市的半價神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半價神也有老爺爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克 是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大地震了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等老頭把半價貼紙貼完大概還要5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絡腮胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在我們的狩獵場可不能讓那家伙亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「大野豬」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則不起作用麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 小狗們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 你們快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠你們是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶發女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒貼上半價貼紙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是全部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 店員先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快貼上貼紙啊 貼紙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是要貼 你就貼快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是「豬」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知羞恥 卻帶著能橫掃「狼」的獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是「野豬」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因為我們不夠成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都想讓老頭幸福地結束一天的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮儀和尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是去買那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 昨天是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...雖然是我碰過的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然飯團還是要吃鮭魚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這邊也...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當雖然也很好吃 不過這個也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還是很想吃便當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然有點不甘心 不過沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是名副其實的「大野豬」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候該講清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心裏是怎麼想白粉同學的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又是這種像是要和情敵做個了斷的臺詞？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉同學是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我想確認一下 這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼想的才會讓她去爭奪半價便當這種東西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是我強制她的 她是自己決定...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才不會積極地去幹這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說 她實際上也這麼做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是 你想說白粉同學認為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其跟我在一起 跟佐藤你在一起更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也沒這樣說...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以踢你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄 也不會認輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白梅梅.. baibai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再胡扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉她今天不過來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 剛才...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,u u u...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:02.07,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}梅在日語裏面讀做ume
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說小梅 小梅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的 那個...是我小學以來唯一的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寫的小說她也說很有趣 對我也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 當然不是指男歡女愛方面的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 為什麼提起小梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才對我又是打巴掌又是踢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...就這樣被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 要等下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11連敗 學姐你太強了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:11:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能成為「狼」就看你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:20.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}無標題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:20.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}今天的小梅很溫柔 但總覺得有點可怕... ..·.（>_<）.·..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪邊啊 看來又要惹白梅生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「風暴」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「風暴」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了迎接春天的比賽而開始進行練習的橄欖球社
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群家伙要是來了的話 便當和素材就會全被他們搶光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去另一家店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強 別勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「風暴」再加上「大野豬」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧 放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那個人是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔導士]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔導士] 是「狼」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這下真不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連魔導士都來了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我在這裡買丼兵衛算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大野豬」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「風暴」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔導士]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...你是說別買烏冬面 買蕎麥面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想要成為「狼」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要嘗過一次血的味道 就再也變不回單純的「狗」了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后也會忍受不了「豬」的屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守禮儀 賭上尊嚴 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓你往前一步的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在老頭貼完貼紙以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點 再撐一會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 老頭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔導士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中下懷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用對手的勢頭 再順勢避開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 是「暴風」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當和素材 全都給我帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？難道說這家伙是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔導士]！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 蠢豬們 今晚可沒有飼料喂你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 不愧是[魔導士]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絡腮胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶發女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[狼]..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能讓你們搶盡風頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「豬」才不配吃半價便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟這群狼糾纏 去搶便當！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月桂冠..就算拼了命也不能把月桂冠讓給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月桂冠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:42.81,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}月桂冠：半價便當中被半價神貼上特別貼紙的便當。視每家店不同貼上各自的貼紙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群蠢豬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是目的還是禮儀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是尊嚴還是其他一切都忘掉了的一群蠢豬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱就該揍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬就該宰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了身為「狼」的矜持 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為「狼」的矜持？ 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書包忘在社團活動室了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉同學很消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是因為佐藤和學姐的關系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝傻嗎？我要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你就做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件？是白粉發過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.19,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}學姐和佐藤同學都沒有給我回復
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.19,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}是不是因為我寫的郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.19,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}很煩人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.19,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}很惡心？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.19,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}如果是的話 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的話 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 是因為白梅她會生氣...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.00,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}寫郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.00,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}To：白粉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.00,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}RE:對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:27.51,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}有來電
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:27.51,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}未知號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 你是惡意騷擾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我把你的手機變成廢鐵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣做了對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 有了 有了 書包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛接到了一個相當繞圈子的像是殺人預告的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉她現在是什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白梅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 難道說你在等我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？算是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說昨天也是在這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次勝利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞起來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味增煮青花魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這是什麼東西才拿的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個便當上貼的是月桂冠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月桂冠？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是半價神在剩下的便當裏面挑出最有自信的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再在上面貼上的特別的貼紙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在存在著月桂冠的領域裏的人都會以這個為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當天得到這個的人會成為該領域裏面絕對的勝利者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次勝利就拿到月桂冠 說不定你能成大器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧 畢竟對手是「暴風」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:20:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 被稱為[魔導士]的「狼」有過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔導士]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是這學校的三年級生 叫金城優
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就先記住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金城優？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 有這麼多月桂冠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一張都裝滿了回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再慢慢說給你聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 自己親手貼上去吧 佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要寫上日期和名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 細細品嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先說「我開動了」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對把它做出來的人 把它變成半價的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及成為了食材的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}還有對那些同樣很想得到手卻被你奪走了的人們的敬意和感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我開動了
